### Login API Test
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/token/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "admin",
    "password": "admin@123"
}

### Get User Info (requires authentication)
# 1. First, copy the 'access' token from the login response above
# 2. Paste it in the Authorization header below
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/accounts/me/
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ0b2tlbl90eXBlIjoiYWNjZXNzIiwiZXhwIjoxNzcyMDg1NzA1LCJpYXQiOjE3NzIwODIxMDUsImp0aSI6IjA0M2Q3YTBmNjA1OTQzODk4NmQyMjNlY2QxYTdhN2RhIiwidXNlcl9pZCI6IjEifQ.lk_QVuRydzrNsEM46ETKC1LJYtiziPYcl1RqCgQLfoo
